OL,3,CShopkeeper calls for 'backup' after
OL,4,Cmaking 50 citizen's arrests in two
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FA Cornish shopkeeper said he's made
OL,8,Fmore than 50 citizen's arrests in the
OL,9,Flast two years to tackle shoplifting
OL,10,Fas he doesn't feel supported by the
OL,11,Fpolice.
OL,13,FMartin Gaunt, 62, who runs the gift
OL,14,Fshop 'Happy Piranha' in Truro, said he
OL,15,Fhas been left with no choice but to
OL,16,Ftake matters into his own hands, and
OL,17,Fhas been detaining suspects until the
OL,18,Fpolice arrive.
