OL,3,CShopkeeper calls for 'backup' after
OL,4,Cmaking 50 citizen's arrests in two
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,F"What we've got to do is we've got to
OL,8,Fuse what we've already got more
OL,9,Feffectively".
OL,11,FDevon and Cornwall Police said it is
OL,12,Fcommitted to working with business
OL,13,Fowners to offer advice about
OL,14,Fprotecting their premises.
OL,16,FThe force said resources are deployed
OL,17,Fwhere they can be most effective based
OL,18,Fon threat, risk and harm.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
