OL,3,CShopkeeper calls for 'backup' after
OL,4,Cmaking 50 citizen's arrests in two
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,F"We will always prioritise attendance
OL,8,Fwhere violence is involved or a
OL,9,Fshoplifter is detained," a
OL,10,Fspokesperson said.
OL,12,FThey added: "Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,13,Fwill continue to work collaboratively
OL,14,Fwith retail partners and other partner
OL,15,Fagencies such as local councils, to
OL,16,Ftackle the rise in shoplifting, catch
OL,17,Fmore offenders and keep retail workers
OL,18,Fsafe".
