OL,3,CShopkeeper calls for 'backup' after
OL,4,Cmaking 50 citizen's arrests in two
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FThe force said it has been working
OL,8,Fclosely with the Truro Rangers ` a
OL,9,Fsecurity resource funded by Truro BID
OL,10,F` to tackle anti-social behaviour and
OL,11,Freduce the number of shoplifting
OL,12,Fincidents in the town.
OL,14,FGarin Evans, one of the Truro Rangers,
OL,15,Fsaid they act as a visible deterrent
OL,16,Fto criminals by carrying out regular
OL,17,Ffoot patrols wearing red utility vests.
OL,19,F"We put people off shoplifting as they
OL,20,Fknow we're figuring out the shops they
OL,21,Flike to hit," he said.
