OL,3,CShopkeeper calls for 'backup' after
OL,4,Cmaking 50 citizen's arrests in two
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,F"Just our presence usually helps the
OL,8,Fshops out," he added.
OL,10,FTruro BID Manager, Alun Jones, said
OL,11,Fretailers should make the most of the
OL,12,Fcity's resources to protect themselves
OL,13,Ffrom becoming victims of crime and
OL,14,Furged people to call 999.
OL,16,FHe also urged people to call 999 if
OL,17,Fthey witness a crime taking place,
OL,18,Femphasising that personal safety must
OL,19,Falways come first.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
