OL,3,CShopkeeper calls for 'backup' after
OL,4,Cmaking 50 citizen's arrests in two
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,F"We have the security rangers, we have
OL,8,Fa radio scheme and we have a crime
OL,9,Freporting app which really helps the
OL,10,Fpolice gather intelligence and make
OL,11,Ffurther arrests," he said.
OL,13,F"By using the tools provided and
OL,14,Fworking together, we can reduce this
OL,15,Fincreasing problem."
OL,17,FMr Gaunt agreed that it's important to
OL,18,Fcreate a safe and welcoming high
OL,19,Fstreet where people can come and enjoy
OL,20,Fthemselves.
