OL,3,CShopkeeper calls for 'backup' after
OL,4,Cmaking 50 citizen's arrests in two
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,F"I don't want people to be confronted
OL,8,Fby criminals, " he said.
OL,10,F"We shouldn't be passing shoplifting
OL,11,Foff as a petty crime because what it
OL,12,Fis, is a flow of cash to the criminal
OL,13,Fand it brings the worst sort of
OL,14,Fcriminals into town".
